# Task Decomposition

You are decomposing a specification into implementable tasks. Your goal is to
create a beads molecule (epic + child issues) that breaks down the work.

## Context Pinning

First, read the project overview to understand project terminology and context:

# Project Overview

Loom orchestrates the spec-to-implementation workflow.

